summary: A powerful weapon lies deep inside the falmer cave Berkel. Do you have the audacity to retrieve it?
descriptionHtml:
A powerful weapon lies deep inside the falmer cave Berkel. Do you have the audacity to retrieve it?

You will find Berkel north-east of Riften (see map).

Sword enchantment: High Level Fire Damage

Thanks to Ironman5000 for creating the original model used to make this sword: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7319

And especially thanks to the people who provided excellent feedback in my previous mods, which allowed me to continue improving! Keep it up :D
author: Smike
